headline: Regency Centers Upgraded by S&P Global Ratings to an ‘A-’ Credit Rating
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Feb. 26, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Regency Centers Corporation (“Regency Centers”, the “Company” or “Regency”) announced today that S&P Global Ratings (“S&P”) raised its credit ratings related to the Company to ‘A-’ with a stable outlook.
